~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : clone                                     ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : clone [<room>]

   Clone will create a clone of you in whichever room you specify.  If
   you give leave out the room option the clone is created in the room 
   you are currently in.  The clone can then listen in to the 
   conversation in the room.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : destroy, switch, allclones, myclones, csay, chear
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
